highlights.text: “反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1531 days straight.
MC 張天賦 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “東邪” is the highest at #15.
“旋律と結晶” by TENBLANK is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #168.
